FK_outfit_006.name: Test Subject
FK_outfit_006.description: She comes as a friend, dressed to blend in. Then the games begin.

FK_outfit_007.name: Pig Leather
FK_outfit_007.description: Pigskin is tough and hardwearing, as long as you tan it before it rots.

FK_outfit_008.name: Deceiver
FK_outfit_008.description: Slaughter is an art requiring razor-sharp wit and deception.

FK_outfit_009.name: Amanda’s Rebirth
FK_outfit_009.description: To appreciate life, Amanda would have to suffer.

FK_outfit_010.name: Masquerade Piggy
FK_outfit_010.description: She realized this party was her chance to prove her worth. The thought gave her chills.

FK_outfit_011.name: Blighted Pig
FK_outfit_011.description: She triumphed over many gruesome tests in her life before. She accepted that she must endure one more.

FK_W006.name: The Saw

FK_W008.description: A tactical blade salvaged and reworked into a highly effective eviscerating tool that straps around the arm.

FK_W009.name: Thorn’s Kiss
FK_W009.description: A cruel blade that tears the flesh of its victim.

FK_W010.description: She seized her victim from behind and drove the knife into his throat. Leaving him with no escape, the jagged blade tearing mercilessly into his flesh.

FK_W011.name: Jagged Blade
FK_W011.description: The knife she bore was like an extension of her arm and her jagged will, growing from a pocket of hardened and bitter pus.

FL_001.name: Forgotten Horror

FL_003.description: There was something real within the pages, as if they told a truth of some kind.

FL_031.description: He fought, and he didn’t know on which side of the battle he’d end up.

FL_032.description: He would live another day, but it wasn't getting easier...

Feng dressed the part of slayer as she celebrated her Laser Bears' victory over the reigning champion, Shock Demons.

Design inspired by Agus Alvi.

FM_outfit_024_01.description: A recollection of her favorite character from a popular fantasy video game.

JP_Head017.name: Salty Mop

JP_Head019.name: Fancy Hat
JP_Head019.description: He pinned a feather he found to his hat.

JP_Head01_4A.name: Crown of The Entity
JP_Head01_4A.description: A crown emanating a festive and ominous aura created by The Entity’s biggest fan.

JP_Head01_5A.name: 5th Anniversary Crown
JP_Head01_5A.description: A crown crafted for a very special anniversary.

JP_Head021.name: Bloody Canine
JP_Head021.description: He wore the mask on his head as he couldn't see through it.

JP_Head023.name: Confused Mind
JP_Head023.description: He drank in the water and looked up to see a great beast drinking from the stream as well. Jake was struck with dizziness; the beast looked upon him and everything went black.

JP_Head024.name: Haute Stare
JP_Head024.description: He watched the models strut up and down the runway, each of them staring ahead with cold, dead eyes.

JP_Head025.name: Mask IV
JP_Head025.description: He could barely see out of one eye, his hands running over the red crystal that was fused to his mask.

JP_Head026.name: Awakening Senses
JP_Head026.description: He salivated at the smell of sizzling street food and started at the sound of pounding drums, feeling both at home and like an outsider.

JP_Head04.name: Sharp Mustache Jake
JP_Head04.description: In what now seems like another life, Jake had a reputation to live up to. A clean look. Suits. The only thing he's still willing to wear from those days is the sharp mustache.

JP_Head04_01.name: Old Man Jake
JP_Head04_01.description: In what now seems like another life, Jake had a reputation to live up to. A clean look. Suits. This is probably what he would've looked like if he continued living the life his father traced for him.

JP_Head05.name: Scar & Goatee
JP_Head05.description: A face fit for a legendary bar fight. What the hell is a lambda?

JP_Head06.name: Modern Explorer Beanie
JP_Head06.description: It's not because you're deep in the woods that you shouldn't look good.

JP_Head07.name: Jakebun
JP_Head07.description: Jake's always been creatively laid back. Look at him transform a lazy haircut into a fabulous hairstyle.

JP_Head07_01.name: Snow Blockers
JP_Head07_01.description: Without these, snow blindness could kick in unexpectedly. With them, you could stare at the powder for hours.

JP_Head08.name: Washed Up Washed Out
JP_Head08.description: First things first… someone needs a haircut.

JP_Head08_01.name: Luscious
JP_Head08_01.description: Long, smooth hair that moves nicely when a hand pushes through it.

JP_Legs001_01.name: Unforgiving Terrain Pants
JP_Legs001_01.description: Stay on your toes with these military-grade combat pants, fully equipped with kneepads. Great for slipping, sliding, crouching, and crawling.

JP_Legs003_03.name: Recluse's Work Slacks
JP_Legs003_03.description: Whether scrounging at dump sites, or constructing makeshift shelters, these work slacks will keep you warm and comfortable.

JP_Legs007.name: Nylon Tracksuit Pants
JP_Legs007.description: Won't rip or wear, even through a whole night of doing the Butterfly.

JP_Legs009.name: Tough Mining Pants
JP_Legs009.description: Hardwearing and tied at the knee, to protect them from pools of underground water.

JP_Legs010.name: Olive Trousers
JP_Legs010.description: Contemporary loose pants for maximum comfort and style.

JP_Legs011.name: Putrescent Apron
JP_Legs011.description: A stained apron that kept blood from ruining his pants.

JP_Legs012.name: Race Stripe Baji
JP_Legs012.description: Loose fitting, formal pants paired with sleek black loafers.

JP_Legs013.name: Builder Denims
JP_Legs013.description: This shed kept him safe through the cold, rainy nights. Or so he thought.

JP_Legs014.name: Silk Stripes
JP_Legs014.description: Luxury pajama pants that match with a variety of sleepwear.

JP_Legs014_01.name: Cupid’s Pajama Pants
JP_Legs014_01.description: An overwhelming number of hearts to display on Valentine’s.

JP_Legs015.name: Survival Pants
JP_Legs015.description: Bloodied and torn into a makeshift tourniquet, these pants still fared better than the boar did.

JP_Legs016.name: Straight Leg Suit Pants
JP_Legs016.description: Slim, silky dress pants matched with a pair of refined, leather shoes.

JP_Legs017.name: Striped Trunks
JP_Legs017.description: In retrospect, a less flashy pair of surf shorts might have prevented attracting the sea’s greatest predator.

JP_Legs018.name: Duelist’s Pants
JP_Legs018.description: Preferring to work on his own, many of his Titan kills were made unassisted.

JP_Legs019.name: Monk Shoes
JP_Legs019.description: A nice pair of black leather buckle shoes.

JP_Legs01_02.name: Universal Command Leggings
JP_Legs01_02.description: The single orange stripe is an obvious homage to when the Cosmic Afterburn crew went back in time during season 4 episode 9.

JP_Legs01_03.name: Heated Leggings
JP_Legs01_03.description: Nothing is worse than cramping during free climb. The sensors in these pants would keep the muscles engaged and loose during a climb.

JP_Legs021.name: Fur-Lined Boots
JP_Legs021.description: He chose old pants from his wardrobe for the night.

JP_Legs024.name: All That Glitters
JP_Legs024.description: It was a silent drive home that night, until his father asked him what he thought of the show.

JP_Legs025.name: Boots IV
JP_Legs025.description: Whatever the meaning behind these clothes, he understood immediately the danger he was in.

JP_Legs026.name: Shared Sparkles
JP_Legs026.description: As the flames flickered against the night sky, Jake felt his grandfather's presence beckoning him to learn more about his heritage.

JP_Legs02_01.name: Leather Pants
JP_Legs02_01.description: The kind of pants that make jaws drop.

JP_Legs02_02.name: Ripped Jeans
JP_Legs02_02.description: The jeans of a troublemaker with boots to match.

JP_Legs02_03.name: White Stitch Jeans
JP_Legs02_03.description: Bringing a bit of rock to the party with boots to die for

JP_Legs05.name: Biker’s Boots
JP_Legs05.description: Indestructible boots for an indestructible guy.

JP_Legs08_01.name: Ivory Jeans
JP_Legs08_01.description: They were originally light blue, but he wore them hard in the sun and heat and they faded even more.

JP_outfit_001_01.name: Ranchman

JP_outfit_003_03.name: Leafy Green

JP_outfit_010.name: Nonconformist

JP_outfit_012.description: A modern American take on a traditional Korean style, inspired by the lunar new year.

JP_outfit_014.name: Winter Comfort

JP_outfit_014_01.name: Heart Cozies
JP_outfit_014_01.description: Silk pyjamas for those who appreciate romance.

JP_outfit_015.name: Boar Hunter
JP_outfit_015.description: When starvation sets in, there’s no lengths that a human won’t go to.

JP_outfit_016.name: Fancy Family Dinner
JP_outfit_016.description: Dressed to the nines, he attended the Lunar New Year family dinner. Exceptionally, his grandmother on his father’s side would be visiting this year.

JP_outfit_017.name: Surf Survivor
JP_outfit_017.description: A survival trip on a beachfront afforded him a little time to hit the waves—time that was cut short by a shark attack.

JP_outfit_018.name: Levi’s Uniform
JP_outfit_018.description: The outfit of an aloof leader from a lost realm.

JP_outfit_019.name: Lucky Stroll
JP_outfit_019.description: An outfit he wore at a music festival.

JP_outfit_01_02.name: Cosmic Afterburn

JP_outfit_01_03.name: Cyberclimber
JP_outfit_01_03.description: Looking almost like something from science fiction, Jake found himself in this outfit he designed as a child, like a nearly-forgotten memory.

JP_outfit_021.name: Wolfy Jake
JP_outfit_021.description: He bought his costume at the last minute for a haunted house party.

JP_outfit_025.name: Number IV

JP_Torso008.name: Happy Ending

JP_Torso014_01.name: Cupid’s Pajama Top
JP_Torso014_01.description: Go beyond wearing your heart on your sleeve.

JP_Torso015.name: Survival Jacket

JP_Torso017.description: An optimist might say the board is half-surviving, but he just thinks of it as half-eaten.

JP_Torso018.name: Clean Ascot
JP_Torso018.description: His obsession with cleanliness spoke to his perfectionist mentality.

JP_Torso019.name: Floral Print Shirt
JP_Torso019.description: He wore a black shirt with floral patterns in a casual style.

JP_Torso01_02.name: Universal Command Suit

JP_Torso01_03.name: Composite Plate Jacket
JP_Torso01_03.description: Lightweight and mobile, it still protected against the elements and kept its wearer extremely visible to spotters.

JP_Torso021.name: Wolf Skin
JP_Torso021.description: His hairy costume kept him warm outside but made him too hot once in the party.

JP_Torso022_01.name: Murder Mill
JP_Torso022_01.description: Vintage memorabilia from a cursed production.

JP_Torso03_01.description: Don't let the fanny pack put you off, this means business

JP_Torso03_03.name: Studded Jacket
JP_Torso03_03.description: If you want to be taken seriously, you have to dress appropriately

JP_Torso03_BroBQ.name: The meat man
JP_Torso03_BroBQ.description: A unique jacket for Jake,created for BroBQ

JP_Torso04_01.description: A bright style that refuses to settle on a single color.

JP_Torso04_L4DInv.description: Thumbs up on an awesome shirt design.

NK_Legs029.description: She kicked at the rubble with her new boots and left the building feeling good about her new look.

NK_Legs030.name: Two-Tone Trousers
NK_Legs030.description: The thought of selling out made her sick, but she couldn't deny that she loved the idea of wearing some designer clothing.

NK_Legs030_01.name: Two-Tone Trousers (Deep Rift)
NK_Legs030_01.description: If clothes make the person, she thought, what has this place made me?

NK_Legs031.name: Boots V
NK_Legs031.description: She didn't know which way to run. The footsteps were coming from her left and right.

NK_Legs032.name: Skedaddle Sneaker
NK_Legs032.description: By the time the guard reached the booth, the only sign of her presence were the words "PERFECT SCORE" flashing on the screen.

NK_outfit_010.name: Howdy Cat
NK_outfit_010.description: Ironic streetwear exuberating personality and making a statement with every kickflip.

NK_outfit_011.name: Reckless Boarder
NK_outfit_011.description: She entered the Xtreme Circuit of Sweden's Blue Summit convinced she would rank among the top tier contestants.

NK_outfit_011_01.name: Powder Surfer
NK_outfit_011_01.description: At the first fall of snow on the mountains, she bought a pass and hit the slopes.

NK_outfit_012.name: Graff-Crafter
NK_outfit_012.description: She hit the streets with her art to escape the mundane life she'd been forced to live miles away from her home country.

NK_outfit_013.name: System Smasher
NK_outfit_013.description: A warrior against the old guard.

NK_outfit_013_01.name: Night Explorer
NK_outfit_013_01.description: One of her go-to outfits for exploring abandoned buildings.

NK_outfit_014.name: Rebel Night
NK_outfit_014.description: Nea was a student of counter-culture movements. Her choice of fashion was an homage to history’s rebels.

NK_outfit_015.name: Beach Break
NK_outfit_015.description: She glided under the rolling waves and gained speed as she crouched, her eyes fixed ahead.

NK_outfit_016.name: Undaunted Teenager
NK_outfit_016.description: To find her bearings, she skipped class and wandered the streets at night, tagging the alleyways with her mark, Mashtyx.

NK_outfit_017.name: Vigo's Disciple
NK_outfit_017.description: The clothes formally owned by an apothecary who experimented with hazardous substances and was never seen again.

NK_outfit_018.name: Punk Rebellion
NK_outfit_018.description: Nea has a couple words for authority and they ain’t pretty.

NK_outfit_01_06.name: Marine Guardian
NK_outfit_01_06.description: Nea stood true to her heart’s cause, tagging poaching vessels in the coastal harbors.

NK_outfit_020.name: Stockholm Art Fest
NK_outfit_020.description: A bold look for a bold scene. Nea entered the Stockholm urban art festival to prove to herself that she's a unique, gifted street artist.

NK_outfit_021.name: Butterfly of the Night
NK_outfit_021.description: The brown, fuzzy fabric of this ensemble represents her metamorphosis from a small-time tagger to a renowned artist.

NK_outfit_022.name: Rhamnusia’s Retribution
NK_outfit_022.description: Inspired by a goddess who acted against those who succumbed to hubris, she used her art to tear down the city’s vanity.

NK_outfit_023.name: Cheshire Life
NK_outfit_023.description: A perfect Cheshire ensemble for those who dare take the road never traveled.

NK_outfit_024.name: Masquerade Shadow
NK_outfit_024.description: She wasn’t sure what the party was about but liked her fancy outfit.

NK_outfit_025.name: Futuristic Glider
NK_outfit_025.description: She wouldn’t miss the sci-fi party at the skate park.

NK_outfit_026.name: Hard Case
NK_outfit_026.description: She came upon a flea market stall operated by a global art collective. Designed by Domrebel.

NK_outfit_027.name: Skate Park Challenge
NK_outfit_027.description: She rolled her eyes when a man with a cocky grin challenged her to a skate-off.

NK_outfit_027_01.name: Skate Park Challenge (Deep Rift)
NK_outfit_027_01.description: She prepared for the worst when something from the rift reached out to touch her.

NK_outfit_029.name: Straight Arrow
NK_outfit_029.description: Tag finished, Nea climbed down from the balcony. When she hit the ground and opened her eyes, she noticed her clothing had changed.

NK_outfit_030.name: Tagged For Greatness
NK_outfit_030.description: Nea would never be the subject of a photoshoot or a magazine article, and that was just fine with her.

NK_outfit_030_01.name: Tagged For Greatness (Deep Rift)
NK_outfit_030_01.description: Her worries about becoming mainstream and selling out felt like such trivial thoughts now.

NK_outfit_031.name: Number V
NK_outfit_031.description: She was prepared to run at the sound of menacing laughter, but the fog caught her first.

NK_outfit_032.name: Virtual Skater
NK_outfit_032.description: She dropped her stencil when she made eye contact with the faraway security guard, and quickly slipped through the back door.

NK_Torso002_01.name: Serious Vandal Vest Top
NK_Torso002_01.description: Apparently, someone has already tagged the back.

NK_Torso002_02.name: Ollie Cat Vest Top
NK_Torso002_02.description: The kitty on the back makes it a bit more innocent.

NK_Torso002_03.name: Urban Country Vest Top

NK_Torso003.name: Svart Katt
NK_Torso003.description: Some say a black cat is bad luck. Only one way to find out…

NK_Torso009.name: Cropped Hoodie
NK_Torso009.description: Warm on the arms and keeps the core cool, so long distance running is no problem.

NK_Torso010.name: Howdy Top

NK_Torso011.name: Summit Jacket
NK_Torso011.description: A comfortable jacket allowing for a wide range of motion that kept her body warm and dry.

NK_Torso011_01.name: Kaleidoscopic Parka
NK_Torso011_01.description: A warm jacket with a refracted image of a landscape plastered across it.

NK_Torso012.name: Tattered Hoodie & Spray Paint Can Holder
NK_Torso012.description: Hoodie with a light, custom-made spray paint can holder for quick, impromptu tagging.

NK_Torso013.description: Skater threads for a night of blitzing the streets with a message in mind.

NK_Torso013_01.name: Neon Crystal
NK_Torso013_01.description: She liked the crystal-shaped logo on her shirt.

NK_Torso014.name: Classic Leather
NK_Torso014.description: The jacket that all the cool cats are wearing.

NK_Torso015.name: Athletic Swimwear
NK_Torso015.description: She suited up to race the hazardous body of glimmering water that could crash as suddenly as it rose. She fixed her eyes ahead and focused on the flow of water under her feet.

NK_Torso016.name: Cropped Top
NK_Torso016.description: Forced to leave Sweden in the middle of the school year, she suddenly lost all her landmarks, both geographical and social.

NK_Torso017.name: Stripped Jacket
NK_Torso017.description: A stiff, stand-collar jacket with a strap of vials that contain noxious samples.

NK_Torso018.name: Hardcore 74
NK_Torso018.description: A hard rocking top adorned with pins from Nea’s favorite bands. Added style points for the spiked wristband and fingerless glove.

NK_Torso019.name: Cat's Claw Shirt
NK_Torso019.description: Cautious with strangers and averse to fake niceties, Nea had a natural affinity for cats.

NK_Torso019_01.name: Painted Skeleton Shirt
NK_Torso019_01.description: The skeletal framework was embellished with glow-in-the-dark paint.

NK_Torso01_01.name: Skull Print Top
NK_Torso01_01.description: Moody top that makes a statement.

NK_Torso01_02.name: Tartan Special
NK_Torso01_02.description: Flashy, with just the right amount of attitude.

NK_Torso01_03.name: Classic Sleeveless
NK_Torso01_03.description: Shades of a calmer place and time.

NK_Torso01_04.name: Rat Print Top
NK_Torso01_04.description: The design resonated with Nea, a reminder of her charming pet rat, Milo.

NK_Torso01_06.name: Jelly Bomb
NK_Torso01_06.description: Watch out for the tentacles—they sting.

NK_Torso01_07.name: Build And Protect
NK_Torso01_07.description: A shirt made for Outpost builders.

NK_Torso01_L4D.name: Infected – Black
NK_Torso01_L4D.description: Thumbs up on an awesome tank top design.

NK_Torso01_L4DInv.name: Infected – Red
NK_Torso01_L4DInv.description: Thumbs up on an awesome tank top design.

NK_Torso020.name: Provokatör Jacket
NK_Torso020.description: An avant-garde dress with a pair of trainers underneath for a comfortable climb over high walls. The streets of Stockholm would not look the same after her visit .

NK_Torso021.name: Faux-Fur Jacket
NK_Torso021.description: No moths were harmed in the making of this jacket. Hopefully.

NK_Torso022.name: Sweater of the Ancients
NK_Torso022.description: Her sweatshirt harkened back to a time when art was made by the people.

NK_Torso023.name: Strange Cat
NK_Torso023.description: NFA. The shirt needs a cat or it’s just not what it’s meant to be. Zzl.

NK_Torso024.name: Twisted Fringe
NK_Torso024.description: The fringed shoulder pad was a bit too much for her.

NK_Torso025.name: Multi-Pocket
NK_Torso025.description: A shoulder bag that won't impede her movement.

NK_Torso026.name: Unique Leather Jacket
NK_Torso026.description: She was glad to find a jacket at the market that fit her perfectly, with a design she'd never seen before.

NK_Torso027.name: Take Action
NK_Torso027.description: His moves were adequate, but she rode with more confidence.

NK_Torso027_01.name: Take Action (Deep Rift)
NK_Torso027_01.description: The thing moved quickly, and she felt powerless to defend herself in this place.

NK_Torso028_01.name: Murder Mill
NK_Torso028_01.description: Vintage memorabilia from a cursed production.

NK_Torso029.name: Motion Unity
NK_Torso029.description: She always wanted an outfit like this and wished she didn’t have to suffer in order to get it.

NK_Torso030.name: Renegade Vest
NK_Torso030.description: She didn't choose a mainstream life. She was a rebel, and that was all she wanted to be.

NK_Torso030_01.name: Renegade Vest (Deep Rift)
NK_Torso030_01.description: There was no rebelling in a place like this. Only the futile effort to survive.

NK_Torso031.name: Tunic V
NK_Torso031.description: She'd never seen anyone wear anything like this. Where did these clothes come from

NK_Torso032.name: Go-Getter Vest
NK_Torso032.description: She was nearly through the demo when she looked up and saw the security guard approaching, stencil in hand.

Plague_outfit_01_CV02.description: Worn for the first rituals ever performed by the young priestess.

Plague_outfit_01_CV03.name: Servant of the Gods
Plague_outfit_01_CV03.description: Worn for the first rituals ever performed by the young priestess.

Plague_outfit_01_CV04.name: Defender of the Frail
Plague_outfit_01_CV04.description: Worn for the first rituals ever performed by the young priestess.

Plague_outfit_02.name: Levant Wanderer
Plague_outfit_02.description: Desperate to appease the god of mayhem and pestilence, the priestess exiled herself from the fair city of Babylon, never to return.

Plague_outfit_02_01.name: Urashtu Nomad
Plague_outfit_02_01.description: Desperate to appease the god of mayhem and pestilence, the priestess exiled herself from the fair city of Babylon, never to return.

PL_001.name: Dilapidated Plane
PL_001.description: After flying through a Bleed, perforated and burnt, this biplane was destined to become scrap.

PL_002.name: Renovated Plane
PL_002.description: As time passed, though, it seemed to be in better shape than originally thought.

PL_003.name: Rehabilitated Plane
PL_003.description: With no work by the engineers, it was curiously back in flying shape.

PL_004.name: Contaminated Plane
PL_004.description: But it no longer belonged to the war effort. It belonged to… something else.

PL_005.name: Moonstone Café Logo
PL_005.description: Mikaela’s café was emblazoned with a logo that was undoubtedly Mikaela.

PL_006.name: Moonstone Café Cup
PL_006.description: Black coffee is on the menu, but black magic is strictly forbidden.

PL_007.name: Meg-alodon
PL_007.description: Her running team came up with some less-than-flattering nicknames for her, but she imagined herself like a shark: it’s only a matter of time before she would catch anyone in her path.

PL_008.name: Mikaela Figurine
PL_008.description: A gifted storyteller, Mikaela was quick to offer a helping hand—be it a hot cup of joe or a mystical spell

PL_009.name: Short-Distance Gold
PL_009.description: She shattered regional records at her last high school meet. Those records remain unbroken to this day.

PL_010.name: Ghost Face’s Camera
PL_010.description: He experimented with cameras as a way to document his murders.

PL_011.name: Carl Doll
PL_011.description: When his coworker called in sick, he reluctantly covered the shift. It would be his last.

PL_012.name: Exposed Film Roll
PL_012.description: A roll of film he never developed. Its contents have been exposed to the light and are lost forever.

PL_013.name: Witchy Old Broom
PL_013.description: There are far more efficient brooms on the market, but it’s not about that: it’s about the aesthetic.

PL_014.name: Dramatic Death
PL_014.description: These masks represent the wide range of human emotion: the joy of killing, and the sorrow of not having someone to kill anymore.

PL_015.name: Gravy Boat
PL_015.description: A vessel with the powerful ability to make dry turkey palatable.

PL_016.name: Crushed Car
PL_016.description: A tiny toy automobile found on the dashboard of a compacted car from Autohaven.

PL_017.name: Acceptance Package
PL_017.description: With a full scholarship for track, Meg was excited to start a new chapter of her life at college. This letter was as close as she got.

PL_020.name: Undead Crow
PL_020.description: Even in death, that infernal cawing never stops.

PL_021.name: Phantasmal Painting
PL_021.description: Is it a trick of the light? Or is something really emerging

PL_022.name: Vacation Crow
PL_022.description: Occasionally, the crows go on holiday to creepily stare at tourists.

PL_023.name: Frightening Stalker
PL_023.description: Nothing appealed to him more than a good scary story.

PL_024.name: Meticulous Stalker
PL_024.description: He planned his murders tirelessly, architecting a death that would terrify the world.

PL_025.name: Furious Stalker
PL_025.description: An underground paper made a joke of him, and threatened to destroy his legacy.

PL_026.name: Chaotic Stalker
PL_026.description: All of his careful planning fell to pieces when he saw the paper's headquarters, and he entered a murderous rage.

PL_027.name: Satisfied Stalker
PL_027.description: Without his mask, or his method, he created a new story that night.

PL_028.name: The Hanged Man Card
PL_028.description: The first of a series of tarot cards that came to Mikaela in a dream. She felt paralyzed in her writing, unable to create or perform.

PL_029.name: The Tower Card
PL_029.description: The second tarot card from her dream. Memories of forgetting her words, freezing on stage, choking flooded her mind.

PL_030.name: The Judgement Card
PL_030.description: The third card from her dream. She pondered what storytelling even meant to her. Was it created? Or remembered

PL_031.name: The Death Card
PL_031.description: The fourth card from her dream. She shed the rules imposed on her by prescriptivist teachers and wrote with her heart.

PL_032.name: The Magician Card
PL_032.description: The fifth card from her dream. Once she found her voice, the audience listened on bated breath, enraptured.

PL_042.name: Lil’ Monster
PL_042.description: Where did they get the tiny body parts to build him

PL_043.name: Megcrow
PL_043.description: This is the longest she has ever stood still.

PL_044.name: Creepy Corn
PL_044.description: Take a bite of it before it takes a bite of you.

PL_045.name: PUBG Frying Pan
PL_045.description: When it’s one versus all, sometimes you have to make do with any weapon you can find.

PL_046.name: Voxel Trapper
PL_046.description: A 3D representation of a terrifying son of a coal magnate.

PL_047.name: Voxel Yui
PL_047.description: A 3D representation of a hardened street racer.

PL_048.name: Voxel Spirit
PL_048.description: A 3D representation of a chilling ghost.

PL_049.name: Hand-Painted Dwight
PL_049.description: A lovingly painted miniature Dwight… but painted by whom

PL_050.name: Candy Spiders
PL_050.description: A delicious gummy layer surrounds what may or not be an actual spider.

PL_051.name: Bloodpoint Gummies
PL_051.description: Do they taste like cherry? Or do they just taste like blood? Only one way to find out. Design inspired by Maomi.

PL_052.name: Have You Seen This Horse
PL_052.description: Maurice is missing, but in his place, a milk carton with a picture of Maurice mysteriously appeared. Design inspired by PotatoGun13.

PL_053.name: Warrior Puppers
PL_053.description: A bright light who will always have a place fighting alongside friends in The Fog.

PL_054.name: Silk Omamori
PL_054.description: It’s difficult to find something that provides protection in The Entity’s Realm, but it’s worth a shot.

QF_Head006.name: Guilty Conscience
QF_Head006.description: Long, restless nights with a guilty conscience. No time to style the hair.

QF_Head008.name: Bun of Curls
QF_Head008.description: She embraced her curls and tucked her hair into a bun that displayed a more mature look, like she had aged in a matter of days.

QF_Head009.name: Elegant Simplicity
QF_Head009.description: A natural style that looks great as is.

QF_Head010.name: Practical, Short Curls
QF_Head010.description: A shorter, more mature hairstyle that displays the grit she took on to defend those she loves.

QF_Head02.name: Strawberry Wave
QF_Head02.description: Loosely permed hair, dyed strawberry blond. Feeling like a trend-setter!

QF_Legs006.name: Muddy Denims & Suede Boots
QF_Legs006.description: Denim and boots for rugged, outdoor living.

QF_Legs008.name: Red Plaid Skirt
QF_Legs008.description: She guided Dustin as they danced, her plaid skirt swaying softly to the music. Catching a death stare from the mean girl who had rejected Dustin, Nancy smiled. She told Dustin that in a few years, he’d drive all the girls nuts. He grinned.

QF_Legs009.name: Indiana Skirt
QF_Legs009.description: A striped skirt paired with knee high socks.

QF_Legs010.name: Wide Denims
QF_Legs010.description: A sturdy pair of wide jeans that allow for full range of motion.

QF_Legs02.name: Tailored Professional
QF_Legs02.description: Tailored pants for when you’re in the office pitching your story.

QF_outfit_006.name: Justice Seeker
QF_outfit_006.description: Skipping school and searching for answers regarding her best friend's disappearance! Not the teacher's pet anymore.

QF_outfit_008.name: Snow Ball Dress
QF_outfit_008.description: She dressed up to chaperon the yearly school dance at Hawkins Middle School and hoped nothing would ruin the evening.

QF_outfit_009.name: Days of Rose
QF_outfit_009.description: An outfit worn during calmer times in Hawkins, Indiana, before everything turned upside-down.

QF_outfit_010.name: Impulsive Activist
QF_outfit_010.description: As Nancy & Jonathan attempt to expose the Hawkins Lab's secret operations, they must admit first what deteriorated their relationship and how to fix it.

QF_outfit_02.name: Business '85
QF_outfit_02.description: Monday morning at the office and feeling ready to tackle anything.

QF_Torso006.name: Sheepskin Overcoat
QF_Torso006.description: Warm layers to track down her friend deep into the woods.

QF_Torso007.name: Sad Cupcake
QF_Torso007.description: The parents of her "missing" friend were still in the dark. Visiting them added a fresh dollop of guilt on Nancy's full plate.

QF_Torso008.name: Red Plaid Top
QF_Torso008.description: She spotted him, her little brother’s friend. He looked as sad as she felt, despite being dressed to the nines. She asked him to dance.

QF_Torso009.name: Rose Cardigan
QF_Torso009.description: A light pink top with a subtle star-like pattern adorning it.

QF_Torso010.name: Woolen Jacket & Sweater
QF_Torso010.description: Traveling with only the bare essentials, Nancy piles on thick woolen layers to keep warm no matter the weather or destination.

QF_Torso01_01.name: Torn Sweatshirt
QF_Torso01_01.description: Crawling into the Upside Down has its ups and downs… like ripping your favorite sweater. Thankfully, you’ll live.

QF_Torso02.name: Diagonal Cut
QF_Torso02.description: A no-nonsense cut for a strong, professional journalist who gets the story despite the odds.

QK_Body006.name: Crustacean Appendages
QK_Body006.description: Its slick body was covered with a glistening, chitinous carapace. Its thorax swelled with gruesome, clutching appendages.

QK_Body007.name: Armored Plate
QK_Body007.description: Rocky blemishes protrude from its body, covered in sticky strings of membrane.

QK_Body02.name: Shackled Monster
QK_Body02.description: There were a number of security measures in place, the chains being one of many fail-safes that ultimately failed.

QK_Head006.name: Hungry Maxilla
QK_Head006.description: A crustacean mouthpart with rows of razor-sharp teeth, dripping with foul saliva. Ideal to pierce, shred, and chew through thick layers of flesh.

QK_Head007.name: Rock Jaw
QK_Head007.description: A stony outcropping surrounding the terrifying split-mandible.

QK_Head02.name: Collared Death
QK_Head02.description: The metal collar is pressed tightly around the creature’s neck, much to its irritation. Three men were lost in the process of fitting it.

QK_outfit_006.name: Twisted Demogorgon
QK_outfit_006.description: The creature was altered by the dark Fog as it hunted and fed, becoming part Demogorgon, part something else...

QK_outfit_007.name: Geo Mutation
QK_outfit_007.description: An unusual mutation formed in The Entity’s realm, causing rock-like chitin to grow from the creature’s flesh.

QK_outfit_02.name: Escaped Specimen
QK_outfit_02.description: A live subject was necessary to continue the research… except something went very wrong.

QK_W006.name: Spiny Claw
QK_W006.description: As its claw dug into human flesh, warm blood curled under its sharp nails. Hawkins Police would never find this body.

QK_W007.name: Crag Claw
QK_W007.description: Hardened chitin grows unnaturally from its murderous claws.

QK_W02.name: Cuffed Claws
QK_W02.description: The metal cuffs were, in hindsight, a bad idea, having done nothing but enrage the beast with even more fury than before.

QM_Head006.name: Perfect Hair
QM_Head006.description: The hairdo that takes forever but looks rebellious and carefree.

QM_Head008.name: Post-Concussion Mask
QM_Head008.description: His face was bruised up from the wild rage of a bully, who had shown up unexpectedly to beat up the kids. Steve was still recuperating from that fight.

QM_Head009.name: The Harrington
QM_Head009.description: They didn’t call him Steve ‘The Hair’ Harrington for nothing.

QM_Head02.name: Scoops Ahoy Hat
QM_Head02.description: A sailor hat for a part-time job at the mall and investigating SECRET RUSSIAN COMMUNICATIONS. Unfortunately, it hides your best feature.

QM_Legs006.name: Dirty Denim & Sneakers
QM_Legs006.description: Luring an interdimensional slug requires slivers of raw meat that may stain pants and sneakers.

QM_Legs008.name: Stop-the-Car Pants
QM_Legs008.description: Steve could have been left behind, but he was brought along in the car the kids had stolen. Dustin had vouched for Steve, who was unconscious at the time, promising them he’d be cool.

QM_Legs009.name: Autumn Khakis
QM_Legs009.description: Well-made pants paired with matching brown shoes.

QM_Legs010.name: Well-Worn Denims
QM_Legs010.description: A pair of worn out jeans that he has been wearing for years without giving it a second thought.

QM_Legs02.name: Scoops Ahoy Shorts
QM_Legs02.description: These sailor shorts come with a holstered ice cream scoop for quickly slinging ice cream to Starcourt Mall's patrons.

QM_outfit_006.name: Last-Minute Babysitter
QM_outfit_006.description: More than a pretentious jock, he's a pretty good babysitter.

QM_outfit_008.name: This-Is-Not-Happening
QM_outfit_008.description: All he wanted was to keep the kids safe but they didn’t like being on the bench. They wanted to help save the day.

QM_Outfit_009.name: High School Hunk
QM_Outfit_009.description: In those days, Steve was at the height of his popularity.

QM_Outfit_010.name: Jonathan Byers
QM_Outfit_010.description: As Nancy & Jonathan attempt to expose the Hawkins Lab's secret operations, they must admit first what deteriorated their relationship and how to fix it.

QM_outfit_02.name: Scoops Ahoy
QM_outfit_02.description: Set sail on an ocean of flavors.

QM_Torso006.name: Pet Finder
QM_Torso006.description: A cool outfit to help a friend find a strange pet.

QM_Torso007.name: Red Nosed
QM_Torso007.description: All he wanted for Christmas was Nancy's forgiveness. Better to apologize than be heartbroken over the holidays.

QM_Torso008.name: That's-A-No Jacket
QM_Torso008.description: Maybe he could have convinced the kids to stay put. He was on a roll before a bully had shown up. But he lost both fights when Billy swiftly knocked him down.

QM_Torso009.name: Polo Strong
QM_Torso009.description: A smart looking long-sleeved shirt from Steve’s younger days.

QM_Torso010.name: Quick Grab & Go Jacket
QM_Torso010.description: Traveling with only the bare essentials, Jonathan piles on thick woolen layers to keep warm no matter the weather or destination.

QM_Torso01_01.name: Scuffed Rolled Sleeves
QM_Torso01_01.description: A relaxed look that Steve wore in the halls of Hawkins High School.

QM_Torso02.name: Ice Cream Architect
QM_Torso02.description: You got the job, just wait till you tell Henderson!

QS_Head02.name: Beanie Quin
QS_Head02.description: A warm hat for those chill Springwood evenings, or just about any other moment.

QS_Legs02.name: Relaxed Pants
QS_Legs02.description: Relaxed cut jeans, a staple in Quentin's fashion world.

QS_Torso02.name: Quilted Shirt
QS_Torso02.description: A midnight blue shirt with a sewn quilted pattern.

QU_001.name: Dwelf Figurine
QU_001.description: The only toy that won't mind being forgotten in the locker.

QU_002.name: Trickster, New In Box
QU_002.description: A collector piece for his most obsessed fans. Look out for sharp packaging.

QU_003.name: Gingerbrat
QU_003.description: It will make you regret that sweet tooth.

QU_004.name: A Friendly Face
QU_004.description: A reminder of the good times.

QU_006.name: Dog House
QU_006.description: A cozy place to hide during the bloodshed. Not designed for Survivors.

QU_007.name: Toy Mouse
QU_007.description: An excellent toy to play with before the killing begins.

QU_008.name: Raven Heart
QU_008.description: A heart, full of ominous and unforgettable memories.

QU_009.name: Home Sweet Home
QU_009.description: Going inside wasn’t such a good idea after all.

QU_010.name: Infernal Box
QU_010.description: An ancient, damaged chest containing unknown evil.

QU_011.name: Maurice’s stocking
QU_011.description: Hay and deep-fried fingers for the Clown’s favorite horse.

QU_012.name: One Million Souls
QU_012.description: Gives a new meaning to doomscrolling.

RO_001.name: Scroll of Toscano
RO_001.description: Vittorio's writings about ancient societies and obscure guardians of knowledge.

RO_002.name: Duke of Portoscuro
RO_002.description: A medallion engraved with a portrait of Vittorio's uncle.

RO_003.name: Howling Fire
RO_003.description: Vittorio's village, burnt to the ground.

RO_004.name: Vittorio Figurine
RO_004.description: A curious man driven to learn the secrets of The Entity’s Realm.

RO_005.name: Porcelain Vase
RO_005.description: Hard to make, easy to break.

RO_006.name: Lucky Coins
RO_006.description: Coins bound together for good luck.

RO_007.name: Imperial Guardian
RO_007.description: They are known to protect from harmful spirits and people.

RO_010.name: Lethal Cocktail
RO_010.description: The warm embrace of a mother’s love.

RO_011.name: Spiked Locker
RO_011.description: There’s no getting out of this locker once you’re in.

RO_012.name: Childhood Memory
RO_012.description: Anna still holds it in her arms sometimes at night, while humming her mother’s lullaby.

RO_013.name: Wanted: Beast Woman
RO_013.description: It says on the paper that her favorite prey is... Humans.

RO_014.name: Elk Antlers
RO_014.description: She kept the antlers among her possessions, a reminder of her past.

RO_015.name: A Dreadful Deal
RO_015.description: The contract Vittorio signed would end up his worst nightmare.

RO_017.name: Broken Mill
RO_017.description: Long past its days of turning grist into something useful.

RO_018.name: Floating Bastion
RO_018.description: An impossible, frozen castle, floating above a winter sky.

RO_019.name: MacMillan Estate Portal
RO_019.description: A one-way ticket to the old mine.

RO_020.name: Rancid Abattoir Portal
RO_020.description: A one-way ticket to a slaughterhouse.

RO_021.name: The Pale Rose Portal
RO_021.description: A one-way ticket to a foul marsh.

RO_022.name: Temple of Purgation Portal
RO_022.description: A one-way ticket to a place of sacrifice.

RO_023.name: Blood Lodge Portal
RO_023.description: A one-way ticket to a twisted cabin.

RO_024.name: Mark of the Carnifex
RO_024.description: The Carnifex would destroy everything in his path.

RO_025.name: Mark of the Assassin
RO_025.description: Nobody could escape the Assassin’s quick pace.

RO_026.name: Mark of the Jailer
RO_026.description: The Jailer was a tireless pursuer, exhausting his prey.

RO_027.name: Guard Company Crest
RO_027.description: A crest that struck fear in even the bravest opponents.

RO_028.name: Knight’s Standard
RO_028.description: A filthy flag drenched with innocent blood.

RO_029.name: Forgotten Shield
RO_029.description: An old shield left on a forgotten battlefield.

RO_030.name: Rising Shield
RO_030.description: An ancient mechanism in the shield began to take shape.

RO_031.name: Dragon Shield
RO_031.description: A mighty dragon appeared on the surface, gripping the shield’s edge.

RO_032.name: Immortal Shield
RO_032.description: With its majestic wings expanding, the dragon and the shield became one.

RO_033.name: Lunar Rabbit
RO_033.description: Vigilant and quick-witted, the rabbit knows how to adapt to every situation.

RO_034.name: Quiet Rabbit
RO_034.description: A golden statuette that attracts luck and mercy.

RO_035.name: Trickster Keychain
RO_035.description: For those who survived the trial of love.

RW_001.name: INNER EYE
RW_001.description: A mysterious frequency awakens the inner eye of those who seek the truth.

RW_002.name: PROFOUND INSIGHT
RW_002.description: The more you see, the more you learn.

RW_003.name: ETHEREAL VISION
RW_003.description: A sharper focus for those who go deeper than most.

RW_004.name: AURIC SIGHT
RW_004.description: Opening the gates of awareness provides perception that goes beyond the ordinary.

RW_005.name: PRO-TECHNICIAN
RW_005.description: Nothing beats a technician who performs the most demanding Skill Checks during stressful repairs.

RW_006.name: NEON ARCADE
RW_006.description: A lively arcade as a symbol for what life is truly about.

RW_007.name: PRO-EMPATHY
RW_007.description: An acute awareness that reveals those in pain.

RW_008.name: FICUS ELASTICA PLANT
RW_008.description: The first house plant Claudette got for her dorm after leaving Montréal.

RW_009.name: Claudette Morel Figurine
RW_009.description: An expert botanist, Claudette Morel was a brilliant science student with a prolific future—that is until she took a stroll that changed her life forever.

RW_010.name: TRAPPER HEADSTONE
RW_010.description: A paleolithic slab of stone bearing the effigy of one serving The Entity.

RW_011.name: HEAVY-DUTY BEAR TRAP
RW_011.description: The perfect tool to ensnare all kinds of prey.

RW_012.name: SADISTIC PUPPET
RW_012.description: A shadow creeping up the wall, an eerie presence lurking. Few know what this sadistic plaything is up to next.

RW_014.name: JACK-O'-LANTERN
RW_014.description: A sadistic grin for a night of trick-or-terror.

RW_015.name: MACMILLAN MINING CORP.
RW_015.description: The corporation that mined both minerals and human lives.

RW_016.name: BENEVOLENT CREST
RW_016.description: The crest of those brave enough to venture through the black Fog.

RW_017.name: BRAND NEW PART
RW_017.description: A challenging mechanical part that rewards the bold and punishes the reckless.

RW_018.name: PRO-NO-ONE-ESCAPES-DEATH
RW_018.description: Hope can be the deadliest trap. Strike when they believe the worst is behind them. They'll be ripe for the taking.

RW_019.name: DANGER AHEAD
RW_019.description: There are many hidden tunnels, caution signs, and blocked exits on the MacMillan estate. Everyone suspected the mine was used for something else…

RW_020.name: CHASER CREST
RW_020.description: No one can escape the clutches of a skilled, bloodthirsty hunter. No matter the chase, no matter the prey, death is the result.

RW_021.name: KILLER STONE
RW_021.description: A badge that signals a profound loyalty to The Entity. There is no greater thrill than to fuel what urges to kill.

RW_022.name: NURSE'S WOODEN HORSE
RW_022.description: A catatonic patient used to play with this horse, until his nurse suffocated him with his toy.

RW_023.name: PUSTULA FLOWER
RW_023.description: A rare flower secreting a thick, pungent nectar during the “Hallowed Blight,” according to Vigo's journal.

RW_024.name: NECTAR VIAL
RW_024.description: A glass vial filled with nectar, which can be distilled into a putrid serum that holds unknown properties.

RW_025.name: MOUSE TRAPPER
RW_025.description: Setting up traps around the mine was easy. He'd watch rodents suffer, squirming while waiting for the inevitable. Suddenly, he had all the power in the world.

RW_026.name: SQUIRREL TRAPPER
RW_026.description: He ventured outside for a new challenge. Each day he'd practice how to patrol areas in the woods to catch more challenging prey.

RW_027.name: WOLF TRAPPER
RW_027.description: Nothing is more fulfilling than to hunt a pack of opponents. This he learned early on while hunting with his father.

RW_028.name: BEAR TRAPPER
RW_028.description: Hunting bears was his next move. They offered a real challenge, being stronger and bolder. He designed a special set of steel-jaw traps for the occasion.

RW_029.name: SADISTIC TRAPPER
RW_029.description: No limits. Everything was fair game now. Even humans... Especially humans...

RW_030.name: INTRODUCTION TO BOTANY
RW_030.description: She found the branch of Biology that spoke to her soul.

RW_031.name: HERBALISM
RW_031.description: She discovered the nature of plants and their medicinal properties.

RW_032.name: PLANT IDENTIFICATION
RW_032.description: She studied the taxonomic diversity of plants, training her eye to recognize each kind.

RW_033.name: PLANT BIOCHEMISTRY
RW_033.description: She began experimenting with plants to produce an array of chemical substances.

RW_034.name: EXPERT BOTANIST
RW_034.description: Her in-depth understanding of each species' uniqueness inspired her techniques that targeted their differences. The specimen in her care always grew faster, stronger, and healthier.

SwedenKiller_Mask006.name: Sanguinary Mask
SwedenKiller_Mask006.description: Drunk one night, he challenged a legendary samurai to a duel.

SwedenKiller_Mask007.name: Snowy Journey
SwedenKiller_Mask007.description: His long ashen hair caught every flake of snow, striking fear into the hearts of children, good and bad.

SwedenKiller_Mask008.name: Horned Demon
SwedenKiller_Mask008.description: He spilled the blood of farmers across the prefecture. No one could escape his wrath.

Swedenkiller_Mask008_01.name: Hidden Torment
Swedenkiller_Mask008_01.description: His sight grew hazy as he listened to the voice humming in his mind—constant, taunting.

SwedenKiller_Mask009.name: Beastly Rage
SwedenKiller_Mask009.description: A battle-scarred bull head, fiery and animalistic in its rage, yet with enough of a human mind to express endless scorn.

SwedenKiller_Mask010.name: Atrocious Disfigurement
SwedenKiller_Mask010.description: Jaw broken, nose sliced off, mask smashed into his face, yet still he fought to the end.

SwedenKiller_Mask011.name: Crescent Helmet
SwedenKiller_Mask011.description: Intricate metal work to craft a crescent-shaped helmet in honor of the moon.

SwedenKiller_Mask011_01.name: Stream of Flame
SwedenKiller_Mask011_01.description: While walking out from the flames, a fire trail furiously floated above him.

SwedenKiller_Mask012.name: Immovable Object
SwedenKiller_Mask012.description: He took the form of a defensively-minded behemoth capable of unspeakable violence.

SwedenKiller_Mask013.name: Shattered Spike
SwedenKiller_Mask013.description: The excruciating pain of the procedure caused him to snap one of the horns from his head in a whirlwind of fury.

SwedenKiller_Mask014.name: Oni’s Mask
SwedenKiller_Mask014.description: A mask he found himself wearing at the masquerade ball.

SwedenKiller_Mask016.name: Melting Candles
SwedenKiller_Mask016.description: The dripping wax sealed the blindfold to his eyes.

SwedenKiller_Mask017.name: Skull Mask
SwedenKiller_Mask017.description: He wore the remains of a beast.

SwedenKiller_Mask018.name: Deer Antlers
SwedenKiller_Mask018.description: The ominous shadow cast by the moonlight inspired terrifying tales.

SwedenKiller_Mask018_01.name: Deer Antlers (Deep Rift)
SwedenKiller_Mask018_01.description: The ominous silhouette against the moonlight inspired fear in the travelers.

SwedenKiller_Mask019.name: Black-Horned Ordeal
SwedenKiller_Mask019.description: Those who escaped in time were forever haunted by the nightmarish image of his black-horned mask.

SwedenKiller_Mask01_01.name: Murderous Mask
SwedenKiller_Mask01_01.description: Some locals nicknamed him 'The Imposter Noble,' for they believed his hatred for false samurai was rooted in his father's ambiguous past—in his own illegitimate bloodline.

SwedenKiller_Mask02.description: His dark and vindictive plan was discovered, and villagers began to call him, “Oni-Yamaoka,” the rageful samurai.

SwedenKiller_Mask020.name: Eyes Of Torment
SwedenKiller_Mask020.description: Death itself lurked in his eyes as he stared down the samurai on her loyal horse.

SwedenKiller_Mask021.name: Plasmatic Frenzy
SwedenKiller_Mask021.description: The fury did not simmer as it once had. It burned immediately and intensely, hotter than the sun.

SwedenKiller_Mask022.name: Sensory Helmet
SwedenKiller_Mask022.description: His eyes shot back and forth. He needed to prove his speed and precision against an elusive target.

SwedenKiller_Mask02_01.name: Dark Grin Mask
SwedenKiller_Mask02_01.description: His dark and vindictive plan was discovered, and villagers began to call him, “Oni-Yamaoka,” the rageful samurai.

SwedenKiller_outfit_006.name: Demonic Force
SwedenKiller_outfit_006.description: He grew arrogant following his recent conquests and believed that his success was destined.

SwedenKiller_outfit_007.name: Ice-Cold Legacy
SwedenKiller_outfit_007.description: The day of Namahage was the perfect opportunity for him. Dressing as an Oni, he was welcomed into homes to admonish naughty children... but it wasn't the children he was after.

SwedenKiller_outfit_008.name: Cursed Fate
SwedenKiller_outfit_008.description: As stories circulated, many peasants believed him to be a literal oni. They feared that an otherworldly creature—something beyond human—was coming for them in the night.

SwedenKiller_outfit_009.name: The Minotaur
SwedenKiller_outfit_009.description: As memories and myths of The Entity’s victims merged in The Fog, a wretched minotaur materialized, unbound from any prison maze.

SwedenKiller_outfit_010.name: Demon’s End
SwedenKiller_outfit_010.description: It was a violent, horrible end for Kazan. Overwhelmed by dozens of peasants after killing dozens of others, he was slashed, stabbed, beaten and left to die.

Swedenkiller_outfit_010_01.name: Midsummer Bloodshed
Swedenkiller_outfit_010_01.description: Kazan was sitting under the shadow of a tree. Flies flew around him, attracted by sweat and blood.

SwedenKiller_outfit_011.name: Fire Moon Warrior
SwedenKiller_outfit_011.description: He cleansed his blades in a sacred pond touched by the rays of the full Fire Moon.

SwedenKiller_outfit_011_01.name: Wildfire
SwedenKiller_outfit_011_01.description: On a red-sky night, he emerged from the burning forest, ready to kill.

SwedenKiller_outfit_012.name: Armored Titan
SwedenKiller_outfit_012.description: A violent and deadly creature from a lost realm.

SwedenKiller_outfit_013.name: Bursting With Fury
SwedenKiller_outfit_013.description: His overwhelming strength made him a priority candidate for testing. The searing pain of the experiment, more than anything, made his rage even more potent.

SwedenKiller_outfit_017.name: Martial Encounter
SwedenKiller_outfit_017.description: He practiced in heavy gear to build his strength.

SwedenKiller_outfit_018.name: Dreadful Assailant
SwedenKiller_outfit_018.description: He discovered the clothing near a sculpted Daruma figurine that looked like him.

SwedenKiller_outfit_018_01.name: Dreadful Assailant (Deep Rift)
SwedenKiller_outfit_018_01.description: He discovered the clothing near a sculpted Daruma figurine that reminded him of himself.

SwedenKiller_outfit_019.name: Mountain Hunt
SwedenKiller_outfit_019.description: After a small town was ravaged by bandits, he eagerly tracked them down in the mountains.

SwedenKiller_outfit_01_01.name: Imprisoned Nobleman
SwedenKiller_outfit_01_01.description: He was captured by a small group of farmers posing as samurai to be presented to the region's lord, but he escaped and killed his captors.

SwedenKiller_outfit_01_02.name: Captured Nobleman
SwedenKiller_outfit_01_02.description: He was captured by a small group of farmers posing as samurai to be presented to the region's lord, but he escaped and killed all his captors.

SwedenKiller_outfit_01_03.name: Ensnared Nobleman
SwedenKiller_outfit_01_03.description: He was captured by a small group of farmers posing as samurai to be presented to the region's lord, but he escaped and killed all his captors.

SwedenKiller_outfit_01_CV01.name: Runaway Warrior
SwedenKiller_outfit_01_CV01.description: He set off to bring honor back to the samurai. He disappeared from home with his kanabo and his father's katana.

SwedenKiller_outfit_020.name: Samurai Eddie
SwedenKiller_outfit_020.description: The field was littered with thousands of fallen undead samurai and he sought the one responsible.

SwedenKiller_outfit_021.name: Red Mist
SwedenKiller_outfit_021.description: A new, unnatural fury took hold of him. Instinct took over, and his thirst for violence grew.

SwedenKiller_outfit_022.name: Night Hum
SwedenKiller_outfit_022.description: He moved through the forest, trying to keep up as his target darted around him.

SwedenKiller_outfit_02_01.name: Humiliated Lord
SwedenKiller_outfit_02_01.description: He entered the battle dressed as a lord and humiliated imposter samurai before exiling into a forest where he would later cut them down.

SwedenKiller_outfit_02_02.description: He entered the battle dressed as a lord and humiliated imposter samurai before exiling into a forest where he would later cut them down.

SwedenKiller_W006.name: Bloodthirsty Sword
SwedenKiller_W006.description: The ancient blade he held as he bled out, whispering one final prayer. But his blood clotted and he survived as per divine intervention.

SwedenKiller_W007.name: Legendary Blade
SwedenKiller_W007.description: When he was allowed into the home of a wealthy swordmaker who had supplied false samurai with his wares, he launched into battle. The merchant never stood a chance.

SwedenKiller_W008.name: Burst Blade
SwedenKiller_W008.description: Carved from a large, ancestral tree, his weapon was the sturdiest ever forged.

SwedenKiller_W009.name: Brute's Xiphos
SwedenKiller_W009.description: A golden sword intended to slay the minotaur, it now rests in the beast's deathly grip.

SwedenKiller_W010.name: Last Stand
SwedenKiller_W010.description: As his kanabo crumbled under the damage he wrought, he reached for his jintachi sword. It too would be ravaged by the sheer amount of bones it struck.

Swedenkiller_W010_01.name: Satiated Blade
Swedenkiller_W010_01.description: He stared up at the trees and reveled in his work. All was silent once again.

SwedenKiller_W011.name: Celestial Sword
SwedenKiller_W011.description: Ornamented blade cleansed with moon water to keep it from rust.

SwedenKiller_W011_01.name: Scenery Slayer
SwedenKiller_W011_01.description: A blade nourished by the emanating darkness of a bloody landscape.

SwedenKiller_W012.name: Hardened Edge
SwedenKiller_W012.description: Its blade was as impenetrable as its skin, and just as deadly.

SwedenKiller_W013.name: Polluted Blade
SwedenKiller_W013.description: The foul, toxic fluid mingled and roiled with the blood of his victims.

SwedenKiller_W015.name: High-Tech Saber
SwedenKiller_W015.description: A light blade with a steady handle.

SwedenKiller_W016.name: Crimson Katana
SwedenKiller_W016.description: A red sword with engraved words.

SwedenKiller_W018.name: Slaughter Blade
SwedenKiller_W018.description: The toothed part of the blade did gruesome damage.

SwedenKiller_W018_01.name: Slaughter Blade (Deep Rift)
SwedenKiller_W018_01.description: The toothed part of the blade shredded the bodies.

SwedenKiller_W019.name: Black Blade
SwedenKiller_W019.description: A sword with a long blade and a golden handle that requires fortitude skill to wield.

SwedenKiller_W02.description: The blade used to butcher those who call him Oni-Yamaoka.

SwedenKiller_W020.name: Ceremonial Blade
SwedenKiller_W020.description: His hand fell to the grip, and he raised his weapon against the samurai on horseback.

SwedenKiller_W021.name: Fell Edge
SwedenKiller_W021.description: Even the greatest bloodshedding couldn’t soothe the feeling that flowed through him.

SwedenKiller_W022.name: Twirling Blade
SwedenKiller_W022.description: He found his target, swung his katana, and sliced through the moth mid-flight. The night was quiet, the challenge completed.

SwedenKiller_W02_01.description: The blade used to butcher those who call him Oni-Yamaoka.

SwedenKiller_W02_02.description: The blade used to butcher those who call him Oni-Yamaoka.

SwedenKiller_W02_03.name: Rain Slicer
SwedenKiller_W02_03.description: This weapon's blade can slice a drop of water in half.

SwedenSurvivor_Head006.name: Masked Rider
SwedenSurvivor_Head006.description: Nothing would stand in her way, not even the potential backlash of a violent police crackdown.

SwedenSurvivor_Head007.name: Pink Beanie
SwedenSurvivor_Head007.description: Unable to see through the thick snowfall, she crashed into a tree.

SwedenSurvivor_Head009.name: Red Stare
SwedenSurvivor_Head009.description: Soon enough she competed in Nagoya to represent her hometown. She gave herself a dramatic look for the performance.

SwedenSurvivor_Head010.name: Sugar Shine
SwedenSurvivor_Head010.description: A hue of soft, seasonal color from hair to shades.

SwedenSurvivor_Head011.name: Head Start Tail
SwedenSurvivor_Head011.description: A ponytail pulled tightly from the middle of the head, rising high from its base.

SwedenSurvivor_Head012.name: Realm Racer
SwedenSurvivor_Head012.description: Wind-swept hair accented with copper goggles found in an abandoned workshop.

SwedenSurvivor_Head013.name: Breakneck Hair
SwedenSurvivor_Head013.description: Long hair that waves like a flag in the wind at breakneck speeds. The hachimaki looks cool but can only do so much.

SwedenSurvivor_Head014.name: Pink Balayage
SwedenSurvivor_Head014.description: Bright pink hairstyle inspired by cherry blossoms to project attitude and confidence on the racetrack.

SwedenSurvivor_Head015.name: Sakura Dye
SwedenSurvivor_Head015.description: A pink balayage to match the Cherry Blossom season and display her ties to the Sakura 7.

SwedenSurvivor_Head016.name: Yui’s Mask
SwedenSurvivor_Head016.description: A mask they found themselves wearing at the masquerade ball.

SwedenSurvivor_Head017.name: Cynical Daughter
SwedenSurvivor_Head017.description: The murder of this soldier’s parents taught her at an early age that only the strong survive.

SwedenSurvivor_Head018.name: Filtered Mask
SwedenSurvivor_Head018.description: She wore a mask to filter out the exhaust fumes on the strip.

SwedenSurvivor_Head019.name: Curly Hairstyle
SwedenSurvivor_Head019.description: She chose a comfortable hairstyle for the day.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_02.name: Vibrant Violet
SwedenSurvivor_Head01_02.description: Breaking free from tradition, she took a chance, determined to defy the odds.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_03.name: Flaming Coat
SwedenSurvivor_Head01_03.description: Breaking free from tradition, she took a chance, determined to defy the odds.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_04.name: Midnight Blues
SwedenSurvivor_Head01_04.description: Breaking free from tradition, she took a chance, determined to defy the odds.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_5A.description: A crown crafted for a very special anniversary.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV01.name: Speed Shades (Black)
SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV01.description: She pursued her goals, no matter how impossible they seemed. Every challenge was in her reach if she worked hard enough to defy the rules that blocked her path.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV02.name: Speed Shades (Tangerine)
SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV02.description: While in Hida she pursued her dreams, working hard to defy the rules and forge her own way.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV03.name: Speed Shades (Teal)
SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV03.description: While in Hida she pursued her dreams, working hard to defy the rules and forge her own way.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_CV04.description: While in Hida she pursued her dreams, working hard to defy the rules and forge her own way.

SwedenSurvivor_Head02.name: Pink Bob
SwedenSurvivor_Head02.description: A short haircut that makes it easy to put on and remove her helmet.

SwedenSurvivor_Head020.name: Bob Haircut
SwedenSurvivor_Head020.description: A classic bob cut with round glasses.

SwedenSurvivor_Head021.name: Fox Mask
SwedenSurvivor_Head021.description: She wore a mask that symbolized intelligence and cunning to impress her competitors.

SwedenSurvivor_Head022.name: Snow Goggles
SwedenSurvivor_Head022.description: She borrowed glasses with excellent peripheral vision to race with her friends.

SwedenSurvivor_Head024.name: Flaxen Rider
SwedenSurvivor_Head024.description: She knew that a week of riding would be difficult, both physically and mentally.

SwedenSurvivor_Head025.name: Snarling Snout
SwedenSurvivor_Head025.description: Some saw the creature as a nuisance, but Yui's grandmother knew better than that.

SwedenSurvivor_Head025_01.name: Snarling Snout (Deep Rift)
SwedenSurvivor_Head025_01.description: Her grandmother had seen the same creature in these woods so many years ago.

SwedenSurvivor_Head026.name: Talent Scout
SwedenSurvivor_Head026.description: She gave the opponent to her right a quick nod and raced off, only to veer off the track and respawn back at the starting line.

SwedenSurvivor_Head027.name: Mind of Ecclesia
SwedenSurvivor_Head027.description: The woman did not react to the screeching motorcycle. Even as Yui approached, she stood still as a post.

SwedenSurvivor_Head027_01.name: Mind of Ecclesia (Deep Rift)
SwedenSurvivor_Head027_01.description: She did not react to the chaos around her. Yui approached, frustrated, and still she did not move.

SwedenSurvivor_Head02_01.name: Vibrant Bob
SwedenSurvivor_Head02_01.description: A short haircut ideal for racing with a helmet.

SwedenSurvivor_Head02_02.name: Slicked Back Style
SwedenSurvivor_Head02_02.description: She dyed her hair a fiery red for the special occasion.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs006.name: First Gear Leather Pants
SwedenSurvivor_Legs006.description: Tight pants that protect her against abrasion. Ideal to quickly transition from the motorcycle to a bar stool to celebrate another victory.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs007.name: Snow Racing Pants
SwedenSurvivor_Legs007.description: Her warm pants saved her from frostbite, but she still caught a cold. It would be a while before she picked up a motocross again.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs009.name: Dark Momohiki
SwedenSurvivor_Legs009.description: While performing, she felt the adrenaline rush she first felt years ago, the first time she saw a kumi-daiko performance. ​She had no rivals; her style was unique and her technique flawless.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs010.name: Short Shreds
SwedenSurvivor_Legs010.description: Shredded and distressed summer shorts, festooned with a pink ribbon. Elegant beach sandals and anklets complete the look.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs011.name: Grecian Conquest Skirt
SwedenSurvivor_Legs011.description: An ancient Greek-inspired skirt paired with well-fitted sneakers for ultimate mobility.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs012.name: Patched Up
SwedenSurvivor_Legs012.description: A svelte set of trousers with lace hems. Bandages seal up any tears made by the pustula’s thorns.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs013.name: Rip Tear
SwedenSurvivor_Legs013.description: Pants that took a beating and the bloodstains to prove it.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs014.name: Reinforced Racing Pants
SwedenSurvivor_Legs014.description: A pair of reinforced stripped pants with pads for extra protection while racing an unfamiliar course.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs015.name: Flowery Trousers

TR_Mask011_01.name: Dual Screen
TR_Mask011_01.description: Pieces of a mask stitched together for an anonymous and unrestrained hunt.

TR_Mask012.name: Winter Demon
TR_Mask012.description: A goat-like demon with a macabre thrill for the holidays.

TR_Mask013.name: Bark Tooth
TR_Mask013.description: A fearsome mask carved from the bark of a dead tree.

TR_Mask013_01.name: Smiling Treed
TR_Mask013_01.description: The cracking of branches and voices echoed through the forest. He quickly hid behind the trees as the intruders drew near.

TR_Mask014.name: Trapper’s Mask
TR_Mask014.description: A mask they found themselves wearing at the masquerade ball.

TR_Mask016.name: Disturbing Mask
TR_Mask016.description: This mask comes from a Lost Realm. He had always dreamed of owning one.

TR_Mask018.name: Tattered Head
TR_Mask018.description: His signature scowl could not hide the scars of many an encounter too brutal to recall.

TR_Mask01_03.name: Freezing smile
TR_Mask01_03.description: The frost makes it even harder to tell who the man behind the mask is... Or if he’s still human…

TR_Mask01_04.name: Smilin’ Jack
TR_Mask01_04.description: A ferocious pumpkin mask that makes other jack-o'-lanterns look downright cowardly.

TR_Mask021.name: Ashen Quake
TR_Mask021.description: A spine-chilling growl echoed through the realm, and The Trapper found his predatory instincts concealed behind a new wicked grin.

TR_Mask022.name: Eye Of Wrath
TR_Mask022.description: He sketched a one-eyed monster with the same fury he saw in his father's eyes. He hated what he drew, just like he hated him.

TR_Mask023.name: Skeletal Shine
TR_Mask023.description: Father's friends were all so attractive and refined. If he was one of them, he would have to hide his face.

TR_Mask024.name: Spiked Helm
TR_Mask024.description: He felt the spikes protruding from his helmet, ignoring the pain as he sliced open a fingertip.

TR_Mask025.name: Frank Stone Mask
TR_Mask025.description: A heavily altered welding mask. Bloodstained and terrifying.

TR_Mask09_02.name: Ravenous Beast
TR_Mask09_02.description: An intimidating visage of a wild, frenzied beast. Who knows what lies beneath? Is it truly a mask

TR_Mask09_03.name: Hoss Mask
TR_Mask09_03.description: The wrestler kept his hideous face hidden, but it didn’t make him any less terrifying.

TR_outfit_008_01.name: Heatwave
TR_outfit_008_01.description: He waited for his prey to spring his trap in the cool evening.

TR_outfit_009.name: Marrow Miner
TR_outfit_009.description: While exploring the mine's underground he uncovered his true nature. Like father, like son.

TR_outfit_010.name: Seaside Psycho
TR_outfit_010.description: The real reason you'll never go in the water again.

TR_outfit_011_01.name: Delinquent
TR_outfit_011_01.description: As a teen he would venture underground and forge his way through his father's mines to set make-shift traps for unsuspecting employees.

TR_outfit_012.name: The Krampus
TR_outfit_012.description: A holiday monstrosity that punishes all the naughty boys and girls. Every Survivor that has dropped pallets and blinded Killers better watch out.

TR_outfit_013.name: Beast of Nature
TR_outfit_013.description: The union boys moved their meetings deep into the forest, but Evan was prepared to track his prey.

TR_outfit_013_01.name: Rotting Leaves
TR_outfit_013_01.description: As Evan walked around the estate, he made sure to double-check all the traps. He had set them up properly, just as his dad asked him to do.

TR_outfit_016.name: Hit The Ice
TR_outfit_016.description: He always wanted to play in the park with the other kids but never had the chance.

TR_outfit_018.name: Naughty Bear
TR_outfit_018.description: A dark fog enveloped him while life’s narrative echoed in his mind, fueling his deep-seated disdain for all others.

TR_outfit_01_03.name: Deep Frostbite
TR_outfit_01_03.description: The harsh winter froze his hands but failed to cool his lust for blood.

TR_outfit_01_04.name: Hack-o-Lantern
TR_outfit_01_04.description: A fun way to hack up your victims on Halloween. They’ll surely appreciate the effort.

TR_outfit_022.name: Hidden Wishes
TR_outfit_022.description: Evan locked himself in his room and grabbed his sketchbook. He knew he'd be in trouble if his father found out, but he had to escape, even for a few minutes.

TR_outfit_023.name: Cash-Trapped
TR_outfit_023.description: As a boy, he would watch his father rub shoulders with other rich industrialists. Nothing about their parties felt right to him.

TR_outfit_024.name: Doom Walker
TR_outfit_024.description: As he set down a trap, something told him this time would be different.

TR_outfit_09_02.name: Circus Brawns
TR_outfit_09_02.description: Step up and see the incredible feats performed by this savage beast! But don't get too close! He bites!

TR_outfit_09_03.name: Deathmatch Wrestler
TR_outfit_09_03.description: As a child, he remembered seeing a scary fighter in a newspaper ad. When he woke up in a trial, he bore in this remnant from a lost realm.

TR_W008.name: Drill Kill
TR_W008.description: An old rock drill, fashioned into a crude axe. Even though the blade is dull, the substantial weight means it cuts like a razor.

TR_W008_01.name: Glowing Cleaver
TR_W008_01.description: He liked the light emanating from his new cleaver.

TR_W009.name: Rusty Chopper
TR_W009.description: He welded metal to create the first prototype of what would become the Cleaver, his preferred weapon.

TR_W010.name: Ocean's Razor
TR_W010.description: The most likely explanation is that this broken anchor can be used to lacerate and mutilate victims.

TR_W011.name: Switched Cleaver
TR_W011.description: A synthetic frame molded for a controlled and powerful slash.

TR_W011_01.name: Analog Cleaver
TR_W011_01.description: A metallic frame molded for maximum, brutal control.

TR_W012.name: The Disciplinarian
TR_W012.description: Used to teach the spoiled boys and girls an important lesson.

TR_W013.name: Hardwood
TR_W013.description: He improvised when his cleaver's handle broke, finding a gnarled branch far sturdier, as if grown for the murderous act.

TR_W013_01.name: Sharp Twig
TR_W013_01.description: He had to be patient, so he waited. He waited until a loud crack and screams scared off the crow. Until the prey was ready to be dealt with.

TR_W015.name: Rock Candy Cleaver
TR_W015.description: This blade will break your teeth, one way or another.

TR_W016.name: Slashing Penalty
TR_W016.description: A hockey stick with a rusty skate blade on it.

TR_W017.name: Crunching Blade
TR_W017.description: A weapon made from unfamiliar scrap that inflicts severe flesh injuries.

TR_W017_CS.name: Crunching Blade
TR_W017_CS.description: A weapon made from unfamiliar scrap that inflicts severe flesh injuries.

TR_W018.name: Iconic Machete
TR_W018.description: A ruthless blade that cuts through flesh and fur like butter.

TR_W019.name: Industrial Club
TR_W019.description: A heavy apparatus that could crush skulls in a single blow.

TR_W01_02.name: Pain Flail (Copper)
TR_W01_02.description: Ritualistic welds that tear and rip the flesh.

TR_W01_03.name: Frozen Cleaver
TR_W01_03.description: A brutal cleaver, hammered by his own hands from the metals of the mine and covered in ice after months in the snow.

TR_W02.name: Marked Bolo Machete
TR_W02.description: A curved blade with a distinctive bulge that adds weight to the fore-blade providing additional chopping power. An almost imperceptible whisper echoes in the wielder's mind: "'anoyk yeqkany'ye hvay'k l'gnoo eydokl'x: sekall'o ammk'ix"

TR_W020.name: Mistletoe Cleaver
TR_W020.description: The bright, colorful lightbulbs made death under the mistletoe less gloomy.

TR_W022.name: Mythical Blade
TR_W022.description: His father’s yelling ceased, and silence filled Evan’s room. He finished his drawing by giving the cyclops a blade that could tear anything apart.

TR_W023.name: Resplendent Blade
TR_W023.description: A blade of shining gold, at once beautiful and brutal to behold.

TR_W024.name: Gnarled Blade
TR_W024.description: He expected to find a sacrifice waiting for him, but was surprised when he locked eyes with a kindred spirit instead.

TR_W02_01.name: Squash Blade
TR_W02_01.description: The weapon used to massacre a pumpkin patch.

TR_W09_02.name: Heavy Striker
TR_W09_02.description: A razor-sharp blade, crudely modified and weighted for the express purpose of incapacitating or eliminating the victims of its strikes.

TR_W09_03.name: Foreign Object
TR_W09_03.description: The brawler would wait until the referee’s back was turned before delivering the finishing blow.

TW_Body007.name: Evening Wear
TW_Body007.description: A dark cape covering a dress suit, fastened with a mutilated angel that inspires both fear and respectability.

TW_Body008.name: Root and Branch
TW_Body008.description: Did the roots grow out of him, or up from the earth

TW_Body009.name: Garment of Torment
TW_Body009.description: Garbs taken from those who ventured too far from their home.

TW_Body009_01.name: Murky Garment
TW_Body009_01.description: He has been wearing this old and tattered clothing for a while.

TW_Body010.name: Charred Scraps
TW_Body010.description: Rusted steel weaves and slices along his body, sharp edges scraping with each movement. It was the same fate as the victims he fed into the crusher, though they had been granted the mercy of death.

TW_Body011.name: Scaly Wraps
TW_Body011.description: Rusted steel from an old vehicle abandoned in the swamp covered his flesh.

TW_Body012.name: The Fire Within
TW_Body012.description: What was once good and pure now burned as an inferno within him. So hot, it would someday leave nothing but cold, dry ash.

TW_Body013.name: Shroud of the Lost
TW_Body013.description: What good is gold when your spirit is dead

TW_Body014.name: Reflective Poncho
TW_Body014.description: Extremely easy to see, except for when it isn’t.

TW_Body014_01.name: Reflective Poncho (Deep Rift)
TW_Body014_01.description: Extremely easy to see, except for when it’s foggy.

TW_Body016.name: Gentleman’s Attire
TW_Body016.description: He was amazed by the noble fabric.

TW_Body017.name: Scratch Mark
TW_Body017.description: One day, the strays clawed and meowed near a pile of metal scraps.

TW_Body019.name: Knitted Plaid
TW_Body019.description: He ignored the flies buzzing around him as he removed the antlers from the deer and closed the trunk.

TW_Body01_03.name: Warted Shroud
TW_Body01_03.description: Wart-covered vest and waist wraps that move nimbly through pools of water and blood.

TW_Body01_04.name: Golden Wraps (5th Anniversary)
TW_Body01_04.description: A once fine cloak now caked in the offal of his prey.

TW_Body02.name: Shadow Vest
TW_Body02.description: Embrace the cold, dark caress of the shadows for they are your only refuge.

TW_Body021.name: Charmed Soul
TW_Body021.description: The lizard came to him in the night, and he knew it was the sign he was waiting for.

TW_Body022.name: Distinguished Wraps
TW_Body022.description: Whoever this was, they were here for a similar purpose. A voice inside told him they would have to work together.

TW_Body02_01.name: Noble’s Cloak
TW_Body02_01.description: A regal cloak that speaks to the wealth of its wearer.

TW_Head007.name: Masquerade
TW_Head007.description: A pale, crusted mask that conceals a dead, yellowed-fleshed face that no one dared to love. Until, perhaps…

TW_Head007_01.name: Masked Terror
TW_Head007_01.description: A half-mask that fails to conceal the evil within.

TW_Head008.name: Hessian Head
TW_Head008.description: A burlap sack with short sticks where the brain should be.

TW_Head009.name: Occult Cloak
TW_Head009.description: A sturdy mask made of bark that allowed him to venture in the woods undetected.

TW_Head009_01.name: Knitted Cloak
TW_Head009_01.description: He blended in with the fog, with his pale and rough skin.

TW_Head010.name: Chain Linked
TW_Head010.description: He returned from the spirit world, changed. The metal chains and plates fused into him, as if memories of his former life as a wrecker fused with his physical form.

TW_Head011.name: Leather Cloak
TW_Head011.description: He sought vengeance for his unjust fate as he waded through dirty water. Leathery fabric scraped the scales of his withered leather cloak.

TW_Head012.name: Shrouded Intent
TW_Head012.description: Somewhere beneath the hood is conflict, uncertainty, and—most of all—rage.

TW_Head013.name: Cursed Horns
TW_Head013.description: The twin growths that burst from his skull caused a pain he could never forget.

TW_Head014.name: Sweat-Soaked Rags
TW_Head014.description: While he should probably have had his helmet on, the sweltering heat made it worth taking a risk from time to time.

TW_Head014_01.name: Sweat-Soaked Rags (Deep Rift)
TW_Head014_01.description: While he should probably have had his helmet on, the unending trials made it worth taking a risk from time to time.

TW_Head016.name: Hooded Shawl
TW_Head016.description: A delicate piece of wool decorated with silver embroidery

TW_Head017.name: Crestfallen Stare
TW_Head017.description: The strays were always nearby, watching him, waiting.

TW_Head019.name: Murky Antlers
TW_Head019.description: He cringed at the putrid stench but was amazed by the impressive size of the perfectly symmetrical antlers.

TW_Head01_03.name: Bog Dweller
TW_Head01_03.description: A tattered, handmade cloak that removed a considerable amount of amphibians from the wetlands.

TW_Head01_04.name: Ripped Cloak (5th Anniversary)
TW_Head01_04.description: Alas cries the wraith, such tears of gore.

TW_Head01_4A.name: Crown of The Entity
TW_Head01_4A.description: A crown emanating a festive and ominous aura created by The Entity’s biggest fan.

TW_Head01_5A.name: 5th Anniversary Crown
TW_Head01_5A.description: A crown crafted for a very special anniversary.

TW_Head01_WinterEvent2017.name: Frosty Eyes
TW_Head01_WinterEvent2017.description: Heart chilling eyes of the cold-blooded.

TW_Head021.name: Slithering Frill
TW_Head021.description: Huddled in his bunker, he waited for a sign that it was safe to come out of hiding.

TW_Head022.name: Spiked Hood
TW_Head022.description: He stood before a sinister figure in a spiky red mask, and quickly realized he was wearing a similar mask.

TW_Head03_03.description: This wax monument serves as a vigil to the final shred of humanity, as well as the hatred seething inside.

TW_Head_Marth88.description: A unique look for The Wraith, created for Marth88.

TW_outfit_008.name: Weathered Scarecrow

TW_outfit_009.name: Night Whistler
TW_outfit_009.description: He visits those who draw attention to themselves by whistling in the woods late at night.

TW_outfit_009_01.name: Space Terror
TW_outfit_009_01.description: He recalled a tale his grandmother told him about space travelers and unspeakable terrors.

TW_outfit_010.name: Mangled Wrecker
